function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	sBossLevelArea = Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(sBossLevelArea)

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	-- If the player dies during the boss fight the version of this on the Start Immediately
	-- fires before the vignette has reloaded. This will advance the vignette quest in the
	-- event that happens.
	Hydra.EventSend("PrisonofCaldeum_BossStart")

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

-- Complete the boss encounter so the fog walls go down.	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(sBossLevelArea)

end
